data.description: Charming 2 story home in River Park Place nestled along the scenic Trinity River trails, offering convenient access to restaurants and shopping in Clearfork and Waterside.  This well-appointed residence features a spacious outdoor living area, perfect for relaxation and entertainment.  Additionally, the home boasts new picture windows that flood the interiors with natural light.  Enjoy efficiency of 2020 tankless hot water heaters and 2020 air conditioning unit, undermounting cabinet lighting in kitchen, automatic lighting on closets, and outdoor lighting.
